     , AMRResult8, AMRResult9, AMRResult10, AMRResult11, AMRResult12, AMRResult13, AMRResult14         
     , AMRINResult                                                                                     
  FROM EQPMASTER , AMRMASTER                                                                           
 WHERE EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = 'R05'                                                            
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = 'Result'                                                                
   AND EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = AMRMASTER.EQUIPCD                                                       
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = AMRMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL                                                   
   AND EQPMASTER.TESTCODE    = AMRMASTER.TESTCODE                                                      SELECT EQPMASTER.SENDCHANNEL, EQPMASTER.TESTCODE,TESTNAME,ABBRNAME,EQPMASTER.SEQNO,REFMLOW,REFMHIGH,REFFLOW,REFFHIGH,RESPRECUSE,RESPREC,RESTYPE   
     , AMRLimit1,  AMRLimit2,  AMRLimit3,  AMRLimit4,  AMRLimit5,  AMRLimit6,  AMRLimit7               
     , AMRResult1, AMRResult2, AMRResult3, AMRResult4, AMRResult5, AMRResult6, AMRResult7              
     , AMRLimit8,  AMRLimit9,  AMRLimit10,  AMRLimit11,  AMRLimit12,  AMRLimit13,  AMRLimit14          
     , AMRResult8, AMRResult9, AMRResult10, AMRResult11, AMRResult12, AMRResult13, AMRResult14         
     , AMRINResult                                                                                     
  FROM EQPMASTER , AMRMASTER                                                                           
 WHERE EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = 'R05'                                                            
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = '   '                                                                
   AND EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = AMRMASTER.EQUIPCD                                                       
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = AMRMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL                                                   
   AND EQPMASTER.TESTCODE    = AMRMASTER.TESTCODE                                                      SELECT EQPMASTER.SENDCHANNEL, EQPMASTER.TESTCODE,TESTNAME,ABBRNAME,EQPMASTER.SEQNO,REFMLOW,REFMHIGH,REFFLOW,REFFHIGH,RESPRECUSE,RESPREC,RESTYPE   
     , AMRLimit1,  AMRLimit2,  AMRLimit3,  AMRLimit4,  AMRLimit5,  AMRLimit6,  AMRLimit7               
     , AMRResult1, AMRResult2, AMRResult3, AMRResult4, AMRResult5, AMRResult6, AMRResult7              
     , AMRLimit8,  AMRLimit9,  AMRLimit10,  AMRLimit11,  AMRLimit12,  AMRLimit13,  AMRLimit14          
     , AMRResult8, AMRResult9, AMRResult10, AMRResult11, AMRResult12, AMRResult13, AMRResult14         
     , AMRINResult                                                                                     
  FROM EQPMASTER , AMRMASTER                                                                           
 WHERE EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = 'R05'                                                            
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = ''                                                                
   AND EQPMASTER.EQUIPCD     = AMRMASTER.EQUIPCD                                                       
   AND EQPMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL = AMRMASTER.RSLTCHANNEL                                                   
   AND EQPMASTER.TESTCODE    = AMRMASTER.TESTCODE
